Ensure AGENTS.md is loaded once; if it was not preloaded by the host, read it now. Then read AI_ASSISTANTS.md, .ai/alatyr.yaml, .ai/README.md, and .ai/assistant/context-router.json. This file is a legacy bridge for Cursor-compatible tools.
For Alatyr help or aliases (alatyr-ai-inventory, alatyr-adaptation, alatyr-add-ai), read .ai/assistant/help.md and .ai/assistant/flows/operation-routing.flow.md.
